stterm (0.6-1.20151220+ff241199) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * debian/control
    - (Standards-Version): Update to 3.9.6.
    - (Provides): add x-terminal-emulator.
  * Additional patches to vanilla "st"
    - Mouse scrollback (button 4 / button 5)
    - Shift-pageUp/pageDown scrollback
    - Increase terminal history from 2000 to 5000 lines
    - Solarized dark theme
    - Change Alt-Shift-c/v to more used Ctrl-Shift-c/v
    - Change default font from Libration Mono to Inconsolata

